```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Browser
    participant Server
    participant Database

    Browser->>Server: Request Login Page
    Server-->>Browser: Send Login Form
    
    Browser->>Server: Submit Credentials (User/Pass)
    Server->>Database: Query User Hash
    Database-->>Server: Return User Hash & Salt

    alt Successful Login
        Server->>Server: Verify Password Hash
        Server-->>Browser: Session Token
    else Failed Login
        Server-->>Browser: Show Error Message
    end
